snippet.title: JUMANJI: The Video Game | US Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Unite in adventure and laughter in the action-packed game of Jumanji, as you try to survive the ultimate challenge for those seeking to leave their world behind! 🎲🎮

Coming November, 2019 to Xbox, PlayStation, Nintendo Switch & PC.

Will you play the game, or will the game play you? Find out now 👉 www.outrightgames.com/Jumanji
